---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 99
By: Ansârî
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Cosmic Dream
  - Union-Identity=Holiness-Universal Man=The Eternally Awake
